E%3Cli%3EThe%20two-time%20World%20Cup%20champion%20now%20runs%20Trybe%20Ventures%2C%20which%20invests%20in%20the%20sports%20space.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMorgan%20is%20looking%20to%20bet%20on%20women's%20teams%20as%20well%20as%20AI%2C%20wellness%2C%20and%20sports%20media%20startups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20professional%20soccer%20player%20Alex%20Morgan%20was%20considering%20retirement%20in%202024%2C%20moving%20into%20venture%20capital%20seemed%20like%20a%20natural%20next%20step%3A%20She%20was%20already%20familiar%20with%20navigating%20sponsorships%20and%20had%20personally%20structured%20some%20of%20her%20brand%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan's%20new%20firm%2C%20Trybe%20Ventures%2C%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20where%20investing%20in%20athletics%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20particularly%2C%20women's%20sports%20%E2%80%94%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%2C%20with%20celebrity%20investors%20as%20well%20as%20institutional%20firms%20such%20as%20a16z%20and%20Greycroft%20getting%20in%20on%20the%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20evolution%20of%20that%20is%20that%20I%20actually%20wanted%20to%20invest%20my%20own%20money%20into%20some%20of%20these%20companies%2C%20especially%20ones%20that%20were%20female-owned%20or%20female-backed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20is%20a%20household%20name%2C%20having%20spent%20nearly%20fifteen%20years%20on%20the%20U.S.%20Women's%20Soccer%20National%20Team.%20She%20won%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20in%202015%20and%202019%2C%20the%20Olympic%20gold%20medal%20in%202012%2C%20and%20she%20co-captained%20the%20team%20from%202018-2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrybe%20Ventures%20focuses%20on%20investing%20in%20the%20women's%20sports%20ecosystem%2C%20which%20can%20include%20anything%20from%20new%20teams%20and%20leagues%20to%20healthtech%20and%20wellness%20startups%20to%20media%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlexis%20Ohanian%2C%20the%20husband%20of%20Serena%20Williams%20who%20co-founded%20Reddit%20and%20now%20runs%20VC%20firm%20Seven%20Seven%20Six%2C%20developed%20an%20all-woman%20track%20and%20field%20meet%20called%20Athlos%2C%20while%20the%20firm%20Monarch%20Collective%20invests%20exclusively%20in%20women's%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Trybe%20earlier%20this%20year%20backed%20Unrivaled%2C%20a%203x3%20basketball%20league%20co-founded%20by%20two%20Women's%20National%20Basketball%20Association%20stars.%20Unrivaled%20in%20late%202024%20closed%20a%20%2435%20million%20Series%20A%20funding%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2251fd3cf5-78df-4284-bb21-3a99aa134991%5C%22%3EA%20cultural%20shift%20is%20creating%20new%20opportunities%20for%20female%20athletes%20and%20investors.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20basketball%20standout%20Caitlyn%20Clark%20to%20gymnastics%20G.O.A.T%20Simone%20Biles%2C%20women%20athletes%20dominated%20headlines%20in%202024%2C%20driving%20ticket%20sales%20and%20adding%20market%20value%20to%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20female%20athletes%20and%20founders%20alike%20receive%20fewer%20opportunities%20than%20their%20male%20counterparts%20%E2%80%94%20on%20average%2C%20female%20professional%20athletes%20earn%2021%20times%20less%20than%20their%20male%20counterparts%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketplace.org%2F2024%2F05%2F08%2Fgrowing-fan-interest-doesnt-mean-better-pay-for-women-athletes-yet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarketplace%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20female%20founders%20raised%202%25%20or%20less%20of%20VC%20funding%20in%20the%20U.S.%20and%20Europe%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20knows%20this%20struggle%20firsthand%3A%20while%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Women's%20National%20Team%2C%20she%20was%20part%20of%20a%20group%20of%20several%20dozen%20current%20and%20former%20players%20who%20sued%20U.S.%20soccer%20over%20equitable%20treatment%20for%20female%20players.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20group%20received%20a%20%2424%20million%20settlement%2C%20and%20U.S.%20Soccer%20pledged%20to%20equalize%20pay%20between%20the%20men's%20and%20women's%20soccer%20teams%20in%20all%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvesting%20VC%20dollars%20into%20women's%20sports%20is%20one%20way%20to%20move%20the%20needle%20and%20pay%20female%20athletes%20what%20they're%20worth%2C%20Morgan%20said%20%E2%80%94%20and%20she's%20expecting%20the%20current%20boom%20to%20lead%20to%20new%20leagues%20across%20different%20sports%20as%20well%20as%20better-funded%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCreating%20new%20leagues%20and%20continuing%20to%20invest%20more%20in%20women's%20sporting%20teams%20is%20something%20I've%20seen%20change%20firsthand%20during%20my%20time%20as%20a%20professional%20athlete%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20work%20is%20creating%20wealth%20that%20outlives%20an%20athlete's%20annual%20salary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Credits%20VC%20firms%20like%20Monarch%20Collective%20as%20well%20as%20organizations%20like%20All%20Raise%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20group%20supporting%20women%20and%20nonbinary%20founders%20and%20investors%2C%20with%20bridging%20the%20gap%20between%20VCs%20and%20women's%20sports.%20A%20week%20before%20she%20spoke%20with%20BI%2C%20she%20collaborated%20with%20the%20two%20organizations%20for%20the%20official%20launch%20of%20Unrivaled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Unrivaled%20and%20Ohanian's%20Athlos%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20VC-backed%20women's%20sports%20teams%20have%20cropped%20up%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20including%20three%20professional%20soccer%20teams%3A%20BOS%20Nation%20FC%2C%20San%20Diego%20Wave%20FC%2C%20and%20Angel%20City%20FC%2C%20all%20of%20which%20are%20backed%20by%20Monarch%20Collective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPE%20firm%20Sixth%20Street%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20invested%20in%20Bay%20FC%20and%20just%20launched%20a%20new%20women's%20soccer%20organization%20called%20Bay%20Collective%2C%20which%20will%20include%20multiple%20clubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Paige%20Hendrix%20Buckner%2C%20All%20Raise's%20CEO%2C%20VC%20money%20is%20finally%20catching%20up%20to%20the%20culture%20after%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%20where%20its%20value%20has%20been%20proven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20folks%20are%20investing%20in%20teams%2C%20sports%2C%20and%20leagues%2C%20and%20we%20know%20that%20these%20folks%20have%20been%20able%20to%20convince%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20to%20invest%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20that%20recognition%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can't%20convince%20an%20LP%20to%20get%20in%20on%20the%20game%20short%20term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c09ffd12-2a44-458f-b360-0ae86b438a86%5C%22%3EMorgan%20is%20also%20looking%20for%20sports-related%20investment%20opportunities%20among%20AI%2C%20healthtech%2C%20and%20media%20startups.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Morgan%20is%20confident%20that%20AI%20will%20never%20take%20over%20live%20sports%20%E2%80%94%26quot%3BHumans%20will%20be%20and%20have%20always%20been%20needed%20for%20sports%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20%E2%80%94%20she%20says%20that%20she's%20excited%20about%20ways%20that%20tech%20can%20advance%20sports%20or%20create%20something%20entirely%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20TMRW%20Sports%2C%20the%20VC%20firm%20of%20pro%20golfers%20Tiger%20Woods%20and%20Rory%20Mcllroy%2C%20created%20a%20high-tech%20golf%20league%20called%20TGL%2C%20where%20players%20swing%20on%20real%20terrain%2C%20into%20a%20simulator%2C%20and%20back%20onto%20a%20putting%20green.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20TGL%20is%20using%20Fastbreak.ai%2C%20a%20SaaS%20startup%20that%20uses%20AI%20for%20league%20scheduling.%20The%20startup%2C%20which%20is%20also%20partnered%20with%20the%20NBA%2C%20raised%20a%20%245.2%20seed%20round%20in%202023%20led%20by%20Greycroft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20is%20also%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20cutting-edge%20health%20and%20wellness%20startups%20that%20might%20be%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20Trybe.%20She%20says%20she's%20eying%20nutrition%20startups%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Banything%20that%