ry%2025%E2%80%94and%20now%20looks%20set%20to%20miss%20the%20third%20one%20as%20well%2C%20on%20January%2031.%20According%20to%20reports%20from%20the%20country%2C%20Pakistan%20will%20now%20try%20to%20finish%20the%20renovation%20work%20at%20Lahore's%20Gaddafi%20Stadium%20by%20February%202.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20reports%20have%20suggested%20that%20the%20PCB%20were%20forced%20to%20restrict%20the%20entry%20of%20journalists%20at%20stadiums%20in%20Karachi%20and%20Lahore%20to%20save%20face.%20Also%2C%20as%20of%20January%2025%2C%20work%20for%20the%20seats%20and%20digital%20screens%20was%20reportedly%20still%20incomplete%20at%20the%20Gaddafi%20Stadium%2C%20which%20is%20scheduled%20to%20host%20four%20matches%2C%20including%20the%20Australia%20vs%20England%20clash%20on%20February%2022%20and%20the%20second%20semi-final%20on%20March%205.%20A%20raft%20of%20videos%20on%20social%20media%2C%20filmed%20by%20ordinary%20people%2C%20show%20the%20sorry%20state%20of%20the%20venues%20currently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20ICC%20Is%20Responsible%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20focus%20shifted%20to%20the%20state%20of%20the%20stadiums%20only%20after%20the%20issue%20of%20India%20not%20willing%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20was%20settled.%20The%20powers%20that%20be%20in%20the%20PCB%20could%20have%20perhaps%20spent%20a%20little%20more%20energy%20trying%20to%20hasten%20the%20pace%20of%20work%20rather%20than%20trying%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20matches%20are%20played%20on%20Pakistan%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20initial%20criticism%20for%20the%20slow%20pace%20of%20work%E2%80%94Pakistan%20has%20reportedly%20spent%20upwards%20of%20Rs%20372%20crore%20on%20renovation%20at%20the%20three%20centres%E2%80%94should%20be%20directed%20at%20their%20cricket%20board%2C%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20will%20also%20have%20to%20shoulder%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20responsibility.%20Which%20is%20why%20when%20news%20of%20Geoff%20Allardice%20stepping%20down%20as%20the%20ICC%20CEO%20was%20revealed%20barely%20three%20weeks%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20it%20wasn't%20a%20huge%20surprise.%20This%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20the%20first%20big%20head%20to%20roll%20because%20of%20the%20laggard%20work%20at%20the%20venues%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%94work%20that%20Allardice%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20overseeing.%20The%20fact%20that%20no%20thought%20was%20given%20to%20keeping%20a%20hybrid%20model%20ready%2C%20with%20India%20playing%20their%20matches%20at%20a%20neutral%20venue%2C%20was%20also%20a%20big%20failure.%20The%20decision%20to%20award%20the%20tournament%20to%20Pakistan%20was%20taken%20in%20November%202021%20by%20an%20ICC%20Board%20chaired%20by%20former%20ICC%20Chairman%20Greg%20Barclay%2C%20the%20gentleman%20Jay%20Shah%20took%20the%20reins%20from.%20As%20many%20as%20three%20other%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20head%20of%20events%2C%20the%20head%20of%20marketing%20and%20communications%20and%20the%20head%20of%20the%20anti-corruption%20unit%20had%20stepped%20down%20citing%20personal%20reasons%20after%20the%20much-criticised%20T20%20World%20Cup%20last%20year.%20They%20were%20all%20part%20of%20Barclay's%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGood%20Old%20Days%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20the%20ultimate%20fate%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20this%20time%2C%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20current%20ICC%20leadership%20group%20will%20be%20taking%20a%20close%2C%20hard%20look%20at%20the%20whole%20fiasco.%20Two%20things%20that%20they%20need%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20in%20the%20future%2C%20while%20considering%20awarding%20Pakistan%20hosting%20rights%20of%20global%20events%20are%20a%20hybrid%20model%E2%80%94so%20that%20India's%20games%20can%20be%20played%20at%20a%20neutral%20venue%E2%80%94and%20the%20overall%20state%20of%20sports%20governance%20and%20policy%20strength%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20biggest%20indicator%20of%20how%20much%20both%20governance%20and%20policies%20in%20Pakistan%20have%20crumbled%20over%20the%20decades%20is%20the%20country's%20overall%20decline%20in%20global%20sports%20performances.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20Pakistan%20was%20synonymous%20with%20excellence%20in%20sports%20like%20field%20hockey%2C%20cricket%2C%20squash%20and%20boxing.%20Three%20Olympic%20gold%20medals%20in%20men's%20hockey%2C%20three%20ICC%20titles%2C%20six%20World%20Squash%20Team%20Championship%20titles%20and%20an%20Olympic%20bronze%20in%20boxing%20came%20from%20those%20glory%20days.%20Athletes%20like%20Sohail%20Abbas%2C%20Waseem%20Ahmed%2C%20Asif%20Iqbal%2C%20Zaheer%20Abbas%2C%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20Wasim%20Akram%2C%20Javed%20Miandad%2C%20Hashim%20Khan%2C%20Jahangir%20Khan%2C%20Jansher%20Khan%20and%20Syed%20Hussain%20Shah%2C%20among%20many%20others%2C%20were%20global%20superstars%2C%20across%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20was%20a%20long%20time%20ago.%20The%20decline%20has%20been%20slow%2C%20but%20very%20steady.%20Administrations%20failed%20to%20put%20in%20place%20forward-looking%20systems%20and%20that%20really%20hurt%20Pakistani%20sports.%20There's%20a%20reason%20why%20Arshad%20Nadeem's%20Paris%20Olympic%20gold%20in%20men's%20javelin%20throw%20was%20celebrated%20with%20so%20much%20gusto%E2%80%94not%20just%20because%20it%20was%20the%20country's%20first%20Olympic%20medal%20in%2022%20years%2C%20but%20because%20it%20somewhat%20quenched%20the%20thirst%20for%20global%20sporting%20success%2C%20something%20the%20country%20hadn't%20experienced%20consistently%20in%20a%20very%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Ruined%20Pakistan's%20Sports%20Ecosystem%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20just%20couldn't%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20changing%20face%20and%20pace%20of%20global%20sports.%20Sports%20like%20hockey%2C%20cricket%20and%20squash%20have%20all%20evolved%20into%20almost%20completely%20different%20games%20from%20the%20time%20Pakistan%20dominated%20them.%20That%2C%20coupled%20with%20charges%20of%20corruption%2C%20mismanagement%2C%20extremely%20irregular%20government%20support%20and%20policies%20that%20ignored%20most%20sports%20apart%20from%20cricket%2C%20saw%20Pakistan%20fall%20behind%20in%20the%20race%20to%20be%20a%20global%20sporting%20powerhouse.%20Many%20a%20sports%20journalist%20in%20Pakistan%20have%20written%20articles%20over%20the%20years%20about%20the%20steady%20decline%20they%20have%20witnessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20Pakistan%20is%20still%20a%20hub%20for%20manufacturing%20high-quality%20sports%20equipment.%20However%2C%20that%20is%20not%20a%20parameter%20to%20gauge%20if%20a%20country's%20sports%20ecosystem%20is%20robust.%20And%20though%20cricket%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20and%20most%20popular%20sport%20in%20the%20country%20for%20a%20while%2C%20the%20sport's%20administration%20hasn't%20really%20been%20spared%20some%20of%20the%20scourges%20that%20plague%20other%20games%20and%20the%20country's%20overall%20sports%20health.%20The%20PCB%20has%20seen%20as%20many%20as%20three%20different%20chairmen%20since%202022%3B%20allegations%20of%20vested%20interests%20and%20political%20interference%20have%20hastened%20the%20decline%20of%20Pakistan%20cricket.%20Just%20December%20last%20year%2C%20former%20Australian%20cricketer%20Jason%20Gilespie%20stepped%20down%20as%20Pakistan's%20Test%20coach.%20He%20told%20%3Cem%3EABC%20Sport%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20kept%20in%20the%20dark%20and%20%E2%80%9Cblindsided%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20PCB%20over%20key%20decisions.%20Former%20bowling%20great%20Waqar%20Younis%20was%20brought%20on%20board%20as%20an%20advisor%20to%20the%20PCB%20Chairman%2C%20but%20then%2C%20he%20was%20suddenly%20made%20the%20mentor%20of%20a%20domestic%20team%20in%20the%20Champions%20T20%20Cup.%20In%20August%20last%20year%2C%20after%20Pakistan%20lost%20to%20Bangladesh%20by%2010%20wickets%20in%20a%20Test%20match%20at%20home%20in%20Rawalpindi%2C%20former%20Pakistan%20head%20coach%20Mudassar%20Nazar%2C%20who%20had%20played%20almost%20200%20international%20matches%20for%20Pakistan%2C%20said%20the%20PCB%20was%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20of%20confused%20people%E2%80%9D%20making%20%E2%80%9Cmistake%20after%20mistake%E2%80%9D.%20Former%20Pakistan%20Test%20opener%20Ahmed%20Shehzad%20said%20he%20has%20%E2%80%9Cnever%20seen%20Pakistan%20cricket%20sink%20so%20low%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20by%20reports%2C%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20this%20time%2C%20the%20PCB%20has%20undertaken%20the%20largest%20venue%20renovation%20exercise%20since%201996%E2%80%94the%20last%20time%20the%20country%20hosted%20an%20ICC%20event.%20Many%20in%20the%20PCB%20will%20be%20having%20sleepless%20nights%20right%20now.%20The%20question%20is%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20notes%20is%20the%20new%20ICC%20regime%20taking%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738231860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fisk5tl3_pakistan-stadium_625x300_30_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fchampions-trophy-pakistans-mess-is-shocking-but-not-surprising-7593526%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20has%20already%20missed%20two%20deadlines%20for%20renovation%20work%20at%20its%20stadiums%2C%20and%20now%20looks%20set%20to%20miss%20the%20third%20one%20as%20well%2C%20on%20January%2031.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fchampions-trophy-pakistans-mess-is-shocking-but-not-surprising-7593526%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Five%20skiers%20killed%20in%20French%20Alps%20avalanches%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22