w%2C%20heartbreak%20feels%20good%20in%20a%20place%20like%20this.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20joy%20and%20thrill%20of%20seeing%20a%20movie%20in%20the%20theater%20always%20comes%20with%20a%20moment%20of%20anticipation%3A%20the%20trailers%20that%20come%20before%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yes%2C%20sometimes%20now%2C%20even%20ads.%20But%20watching%20these%2C%20that's%20just%20part%20of%20the%20experience%2C%20right%3F%20We%20go%20in%20knowing%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20few%20minutes%20before%20the%20movie%20starts.%20As%20a%20chronically%20late%20person%2C%20I%20find%20this%20buffer%20of%20an%20extra%2010%20or%20so%20minutes%20useful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20lawmaker%20from%20Connecticut%20is%20trying%20to%20change%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20Sen.%20Martin%20M.%20Looney%2C%20a%20Democrat%20representing%20New%20Haven%20in%20the%20Connecticut%20State%20Senate%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cga.ct.gov%2F2025%2FTOB%2FS%2FPDF%2F2025SB-00797-R00-SB.PDF%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20proposed%20a%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20require%20movie%20theaters%20to%20list%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ereal%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0start%20times%20of%20a%20movie%20%E2%80%94%20not%20when%20the%20trailers%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20a%20theater's%20website%20would%20have%20to%20list%20both%20the%20time%20the%20ads%20or%20trailers%20begin%20and%20the%20time%20the%20actual%20film%20begins%20%E2%80%94%20something%20like%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BA%20Complete%20Unknown%26quot%3B%207%3A00%20p.m.%20(film%20starts%20at%207%3A08%20p.m.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooney%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%2C%20but%20he%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.registercitizen.com%2Fconnecticut%2Farticle%2Fct-movie-theater-start-times-previews-film-looney-20048796.php%3Fcmpid%3Dfbsocialflow%26fbclid%3DIwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAR0INYF46-jXSgy5xn8C06G7aBh2yrsGMsEz-SZD0sSXNdslQI-3fYkjsw0_aem_8izRqt_7jE4YxgkO6qYwVQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERegister%20Citizen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20first%20reported%20on%20the%20bill%3Cem%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20abuse%20of%20people's%20time.%20If%20they%20want%20to%20get%20there%20early%20and%20watch%20the%20promos%2C%20they%20can.%20But%20if%20they%20just%20want%20to%20see%20the%20feature%2C%20they%20ought%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20there%20just%20in%20time%20for%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20we've%20all%20been%20slightly%20frustrated%20having%20to%20sit%20through%20not%20just%20trailers%20but%20also%20regular%20advertisements%20when%20we%20paid%20for%20a%20ticket%20just%20to%20see%20a%20movie.%20But%20to%20me%2C%20sitting%20through%20the%20previews%20feels%20like%20a%20small%20price%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20pleasures%20of%20moviegoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Although%20like%20much%20in%20politics%2C%20it's%20a%20divisive%20issue.%20Several%20of%20my%20colleagues%20%3Cem%3Elove%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20idea%20of%20knowing%20a%20movie's%20true%20start%20time.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAds%20and%20trailers%20also%20are%20a%20part%20of%20revenue%20for%20some%20theaters%20at%20a%20time%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmovie-industry-inflection-point-barbie-oppenheimer-mario-success-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emovie%20ticket%20sales%20have%20not%20recovered%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20start%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20as%20streaming%20has%20eaten%20into%20their%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Theatre%20Owners%20declined%20to%20comment%20about%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trailers%20before%20the%20main%20attraction%20also%20allow%20movie%20lovers%20to%20learn%20about%20new%20movies.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchart-na1.emarketer.com%2F268758%2Fchannels-adults-canada-us-usually-notice-promotional-campaigns-new-movies-movie-theaters-may-2024-of-respondents%5C%22%20target%3