erica%2C%20for%20the%20deal.%20CEO%20Owen%20Tripp%20confirmed%20to%20BI%20this%20month%20that%20the%20startup%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20filed%20its%20S-1%20privately%20for%20an%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncluded%2C%20formed%20when%20care%20navigator%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrand-rounds-doctor-on-demand-are-acquiring-included-health-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrand%20Rounds%20and%20virtual%20care%20provider%20Doctor%20on%20Demand%20merged%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%202021%2C%20works%20with%20companies%20to%20help%20employees%20navigate%20their%20benefits%20and%20access%20services%20like%20virtual%20care%20and%20mental%20healthcare.%20The%20startup%20hoped%20to%20join%20a%20surging%20class%20of%20public%20healthtech%20companies%20%E2%80%94%C2%A023%20healthcare%20startups%20went%20public%20via%20IPO%20or%20SPAC%20in%202021%2C%20per%20Rock%20Health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-fed-taper-rate-hike-pulls-support-wolfenbarger-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eend%20of%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%2C%20the%20market%20had%20already%20begun%20to%20take%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%2C%20dampening%20Included's%20IPO%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%20the%20writing%20on%20the%20wall%2C%20Tripp%20said%20he%20pulled%20Included%20out%20of%20its%20planned%20%26quot%3Btest%20the%20waters%26quot%3B%20meetings%20with%20potential%20investors%2C%20and%20the%20startup%20took%20a%20step%20back%20to%20reevaluate%20its%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20spent%20most%20of%20that%20intervening%20time%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20had%20a%20really%20strong%20cash%20position%20%E2%80%94%20we%20didn't%20need%20to%20raise%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Tripp%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20could%20really%20look%20hard%20in%20the%20mirror%20at%20what%20we%20liked%20and%20what%20we%20didn't%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20Included%20Health%20liked%2C%20Tripp%20said%2C%20was%20its%20ability%20to%20provide%20healthcare%20that%20patients%20trusted.%20What%20needed%20work%20was%20its%20ability%20to%20provide%20personalized%20care%20integrated%20with%20help%20for%20employees%20seeking%20more%20than%20just%20a%20doctor's%20visit%2C%20like%20those%20juggling%20multiple%20types%20of%20care%20and%20facing%20administrative%20headaches%20like%20denied%20insurance%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20that%20more%20effectively%2C%20the%20startup%20restructured%20its%20executive%20team%20including%20through%20new%20CFO%20and%20chief%20legal%20officer%20hires%2C%C2%A0began%20building%20new%20products%2C%20and%20became%20profitable%2C%20Tripp%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Included%20didn't%20disclose%20its%20current%20revenue%2C%20the%20startup%20said%20it's%20seen%20double-digit%20revenue%20growth%20since%202021%20and%20now%20works%20with%20about%20300%20employers%20and%20health%20plans.%20Four%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20company%20had%20about%20250%20contracts%20and%20combined%20revenue%20in%20the%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincluded-health-formerly-grand-rounds-ipo-2022-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eafter%20the%20Grand%20Rounds-Doctor%20on%20Demand%20merger%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20also%20expanded%20existing%20contracts%20like%20its%20deal%20with%20Walmart%2C%20and%20landed%20new%20ones%2C%20including%20with%20the%20California%20Public%20Employees'%20Retirement%20System.%20It's%20now%20working%20with%20about%20300%20employers%20and%20health%20plans.%20Tripp%20called%20the%20CalPERS%20tie-in%2C%20announced%20in%20June%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20deal%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20strong%20positive%20signal%20of%20the%20healthcare%20market's%20appetite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20part%20of%20my%20optimism%20about%20why%20companies%20like%20ours%20are%20much%20stronger%20in%20this%20cycle%20than%20any%20of%20the%20compa