sistants%20carefully%20to%20level%20up%20clinicians%20rather%20than%20replace%20them.%20He%20also%20teased%20that%20Included%20would%20soon%20push%20into%20home%20care%20and%20pharmacy%20support%20to%20further%20its%20vision%20of%20integrated%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETripp%20told%20BI%20that%20Included%20doesn't%20have%20any%20preference%20on%20its%20cap%20table%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0all%20of%20its%20shares%20are%20common%20stock%2C%20meaning%20in%20the%20event%20of%20an%20exit%2C%20its%20investors%20will%20get%20equal%20rights%20to%20their%20payouts.%20He%20says%20that%20allows%20Included%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20function%20more%20like%20a%20public%20company%20than%20some%20other%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20some%20point%2C%20we%20want%20to%20reward%20people%20with%20liquidity%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20driving%20force%20of%20what%20we%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincluded-health-profitable-growing-2022-ipo-plans-go-public-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738231202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67990daa7bb3f854015aac21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincluded-health-profitable-growing-2022-ipo-plans-go-public-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Included%20Health%20filed%20its%20S-1%20for%20an%20IPO%20that%20never%20happened.%20Its%20CEO%20said%20the%20company%20went%20heads-down%20to%20reach%20profitability%20and%20sales%20growth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rtorrence%40businessinsider.com%20(Rebecca%20Torrence)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincluded-health-profitable-growing-2022-ipo-plans-go-public-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20Amazon's%20plan%20to%20cut%20managers%3A%20More%20direct%20reports