0record%20amount%20of%20the%20stock%20during%20Monday's%20rout%2C%20snapping%20up%20a%20net%20%24562%20million%20worth%20of%20Nvidia%20shares%2C%20VandaTrack%20Research%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20According%20to%20data%20stretching%20back%20to%202014%2C%20that%20represents%20the%20largest%20single-day%20inflow%20to%20Nvidia%20from%20retail%20traders%20in%20at%20least%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVanda%20said%20the%20buying%20spree%20continued%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20with%20retail%20investors%20purchasing%20a%20net%20%24921%20million%20worth%20of%20Nvidia%20shares%20in%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20clawed%20back%20some%20losses%20in%20Tuesday's%20session%2C%20rising%20about%209%25%2C%20but%20was%20down%20almost%205%25%20Wednesday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20traders%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20said%20they%20had%20remained%20confident%20in%20the%20chipmaker%20and%20were%20planning%20to%20buy%20the%20dip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShade%20Gotau%2C%20a%20retail%20trader%20who%20began%20investing%20in%20Nvidia%20in%202023%2C%20says%20she's%20invested%20in%20the%20chipmaker%20for%20the%20long%20haul%20and%20isn't%20shaken%20by%20the%20recent%20sell-off.%20In%20her%20view%2C%20fluctuations%20in%20the%20stock%20are%20normal%2C%20and%20she%20plans%20to%20keep%20purchasing%20more%20shares%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recent%20market%20sell-off%20didn't%20shake%20my%20confidence%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI%2C%20calling%20the%20recent%20decline%20a%20%26quot%3Bprime%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20stock%20continues%20to%20dip%2C%20I'll%20be%20there%20to%20buy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestdiva.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKiana%20Danial%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20another%20retail%20trader%20who%20began%20investing%20in%20Nvidia%20in%202016%20and%20had%20sold%20some%20of%20her%20shares%20to%20help%20fund%20a%20down%20payment%20on%20a%20home%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ealso%20brushed%20off%20the%20losses%20and%20said%20she%20bought%20the%20dip%20as%20the%20stock%20sold%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20has%20weathered%20bouts%20of%20pain%20before%2C%20she%20noted%2C%20pointing%20to%202022%2C%20when%20shares%20plunged%2050%25%20amid%20a%20broader%20bear%20market%20plunge%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20that's%20to%20say%2C%20long-term%20investors%20should%20not%20get%20shaken%20by%20temporary%20market%20hiccups%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Danial%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20bought%20more.%20I%20am%20planning%20to%20buy%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDanial%20said%20she%20doubted%20the%20lasting%20impact%20of%20DeepSeek%2C%20the%20AI%20app%20from%20a%20Chinese%20startup%20that%20has%20upended%20Wall%20Street's%20view%20of%20the%20AI%20boom%20this%20week.%20She%20questioned%20whether%20the%20company's%20model%20was%20comparable%20to%20US%20rivals'%20trained%20on%20superior%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20everything%20that%20so%20far%20we%20know%20about%20this%2C%20first%20of%20all%2C%20is%20based%20on%20what%20they%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20DeepSeek's%20debut%20last%20week.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fundamentals%20of%20a%20rock%20solid%20company%20like%20Nvidia%20or%20even%20Microsoft%2C%20they%20don't%20just%20crumble%20because%20a%20competitor%20showed%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20retail%20trader%20Kaihan%20Toofan%20also%20questioned%20DeepSeek's%20ability%20to%20compete%20with%20larger%20US%20peers.%20In%20his%20opinion%2C%20DeepSeek's%20move%20to%20disrupt%20established%20players%20in%20the%20space%20is%20%26quot%3Blaughable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20stepping%20into%20a%20battlefield%20dominated%20by%20giants%20who%20have%20been%20promoting%20and%20refining%20AI%20technologies%20for%20years%2C%20pouring%20billions%20into%20research%20and%20development.%20Their%20efforts%20seem%20amateurish%20at%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToofan%20isn't%20investing%20in%20Nvidia%20for%20the%20long%20term%2C%20but%20he%20holds%20some%20shares%20and%20plans%20to%20acquire%20more%2C%20as%20he%20believes%20the%20sell-off%20was%20an%20overreaction%20from%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20be%20buying%20a%20lot%20once%20the%20market%20starts%20to%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20slew%20of%20mega-cap%20tech%20earnings%20coming%20out%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrace%20Graham%2C%20an%20investor%20who%20first%20purchased%20Nvidia%20about%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20said%20the%20stock%20looked%20expensive%20prior%20to%20its%20sell-off%20on%20Monday%2C%20but%20the%20sharp%20pullback%20looks%20like%20an%20attractive%20entry%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20bubble%20definitely%20did%20pop%20and%20I%20think%20that%20the%20market%20was%20a%20little%20overpriced.%20I%20think%20we%20got%20a%20really%20big%20reality%20check%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20the%20worst%20thing.%20And%20I%20think%20it'll%20pick%20back%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20would%20also%20hold%20onto%20his%20existing%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prospect%20of%20the%20stock%20seeing%20a%20more%20pronounced%20sell-off%20also%20doesn't%20concern%20Graham.%20Like%20other%20traders%20who%20spoke%20with%20BI%2C%20he%20also%20doesn't%20see%20DeepSeek%20as%20all%20that%20threatening%20to%20the%20AI%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Nvidia%20is%20still%20super%20powerful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20DeepSeek%20was%20trained%20using%20older%2C%20less%20powerful%20Nvidia%20chips.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20a%20good%20thing%2C%20and%20I%20think%20eventually%20Nvidia%20will%20be%20back%20to%20where%20it%20was%2C%20probably%20even%20more.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%2C%20in%20his%20view%2C%20Nvidia%20would%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20top%20provider%20of%20chips%20for%20other%20countries%20and%20companies%20working%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20D.%2C%20an%20investor%20who%20started%20buying%20Nvidia%20stock%20several%20years%20ago%2C%20said%20he%20plans%20to%20keep%20it%20as%20long%20as%20he%20lives%20so%20that%20his%20children%20can%20get%20the%20shares%20tax-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bgut-wrenching%26quot%3B%20to%20see%20the%20stock%20plummet%20on%20Monday.%20However%2C%20when%20he%20looked%20into%20it%20more%20and%20caught%20up%20on%20the%20DeepSeek%20news%2C%20he%20wasn't%20as%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNvidia%20is%20booked%20solid%20for%20quarters%20on%20their%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20Downs%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20doesn't%20see%20the%20company's%20dominance%20slipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20is%20the%20poster%20child%20of%20the%20AI%20trade%2C%20and%20the%20stock%20has%20risen%202000%25%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20Even%20as%20some%20forecasters%20have%20been%20sounding%20the%20alarm%20on%20the%20potential%20for%20a%20larger%20pullback%2C%20Wall%20Street's%20bull%20case%20for%20the%20stock%20and%20the%20tech%20sector%20seems%20to%20be%20intact%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20sell-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20there%20is%20only%20one%20chip%20company%20in%20the%20world%20launching%20autonomous%2C%20robotics%2C%20and%20broader%20AI%20use%20cases%20and%20that%20is%20Nvidia%2C%26quot%3B%20Wedbush%20Securities%20analyst%20Dan%20Ives%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20following%20Monday's%20decline.%20%26quot%3BLaunching%20broader%20AI%20infrastructure%20is%20a%20whole%20other%20ballgame%20and%20nothing%20with%20DeepSeek%20makes%20us%20believe%20anything%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-crash-tech-selloff-ai-chips-gpu-deepseek-traders-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738231202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679a91db196626c40985b484%