%3E%20to%20be%20delivered%20by%20Finance%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fnirmala-sitharaman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENirmala%20Sitharaman%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20had%20been%20reports%20the%20new%20tax%20code%2C%20or%20DTC%2C%20would%20be%20read%20out%20with%20the%20budget%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalk%20of%20a%20new%20direct%20tax%20code%20emerged%20when%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20presented%20the%20full%202024%2F25%20budget%20in%20July%3B%20then%20she%20had%20said%20the%20goal%20was%20to%20make%20current%20income%20tax%20laws%20simpler%20to%20read%20and%20understand%2C%20and%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20pages%20of%20the%20I-T%20Act%20of%201961%20by%20a%20staggering%2060%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201961%20Act%20-%20which%20deals%20with%20imposition%20of%20direct%20taxes%2C%20i.e.%2C%20personal%20and%20corporate%20tax%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20on%20securities%20transactions%2C%20gifts%2C%20and%20wealth%20-%20has%2023%20chapters%20and%20298%20sections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20calculating%20tax%20amount%20and%20filing%20returns%20easier%20and%2C%20among%20the%20biggest%20likely%20changes%2C%20will%20also%20scrap%20the%20concept%20of%20financial%20year%20(FY)%20vis-a-vis%20accounting%20year%20(AY).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20talk%20of%20a%20flat%2015%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20dividends%20earned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20then%20had%20said%20the%20new%20revised%20law%20would%20be%20introduced%20in%20the%20next%20Budget%20session%20of%20Parliament%2C%20i.e.%2C%20which%20begins%20Friday%20with%20the%20tabling%20of%20the%20annual%20economic%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20had%20announced%20the%20overhaul%20of%20the%20I-T%20Act%2C%20the%20CBDT%2C%20or%20Central%20Board%20of%20Direct%20Taxes%20set%20up%20an%20internal%20committee%20to%20oversee%20the%20review%3B%20this