20people%20around%20her.%20It%20was%20interesting%20for%20her.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20expect%20or%20ask%20for%20payment%20for%20the%20therapy%20sessions%2C%20yet%20people%20would%20invariably%20get%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20from%20their%20land%20as%20payment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20place%20where%20words%20find%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriters%20were%20encouraged%20to%20write%20in%20any%20form%2C%20whether%20poetry%2C%20fiction%2C%20or%20non-fiction.%20The%20workshops%20led%20by%20eminent%20authors%20were%20big%20hits%20and%20on%20the%20rise%20until%20COVID-19%20struck.%20The%20onsite%20workshops%20had%20to%20stop%2C%20as%20did%20the%20whole%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-4_11zon-1737754794.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vandita%20Dubey%20and%20Chetan%20Mahajan%20founded%20Himalayan%20Writing%20Retreat%20in%202016%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-4_11zon-1737754794.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-4_11zon-1737754794-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-4_11zon-1737754794-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-4_11zon-1737754794-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025